WEBVTT

00:01:58.757 --> 00:02:00.269
Today, one says,

00:02:00.293 --> 00:02:02.380
"Give us today our daily bread."

00:02:02.404 --> 00:02:04.130
In Old English, they said,

00:02:04.154 --> 00:02:07.415
"Urne gedaeghwamlican
hlaf syle us todaeg."

00:02:09.148 --> 00:02:11.121
Things change in conlangs, too.

00:02:11.438 --> 00:02:14.578
Tolkien charted out ancient
and newer versions of Elvish.

